@startuml
participant "System Orchestrator" as System
participant "Groq API Layer" as AI
participant "Data Store (JSON)" as DB

== Phase 2: AI Role Discovery ==
System -> AI: Profile JSON + Instruct to suggest roles
AI --> System: 8 Target Roles (JSON)
System -> DB: Return to User & Save

== Phase 3: Research Persona Synthesis ==
System -> AI: Parsed LinkedIn posts & Company Info
AI --> System: Synthesized Hiring Persona (JSON)
System -> DB: Save schema bounded macro-persona metadata

== Phase 4: GAN Document Generation Loop ==
loop Until Quality Score >= 9.0 (Max 5x)
  System -> AI (Agent A - Generator): Generate targeted CV based on computed Persona
  AI (Agent A) --> System: Raw CV Draft JSON
  System -> AI (Agent B - Discriminator): Scrutinize CV explicitly against Persona
  AI (Agent B) --> System: Output critical Score & Edit flags
end
System -> DB: Compile & Serialize final optimized CV JSON

== Phase 7: Stateful Interview Simulation ==
System -> AI: System Prompt + Core Persona logic context
AI --> System: Returns native introductory question
loop Interview Active Ping-Pong
  System -> AI: Candidate message + Append chat transcript
  AI --> System: Generates authenticated Persona Reaction natively maintaining constraints
end
System -> AI: Terminate simulation. Aggregate historical run.
AI --> System: Detailed scoring output + Metrics
System -> DB: Archive transcript log & append feedback metrics.
@enduml
